column2: SELECT n.distance, m.*, o.*, spec.*, f.gain_u, f.gain_g, f.gain_r, f.gain_i, f.gain_z, f.saturationLevel_u , f.saturationLevel_g, f.saturationLevel_r, f.saturationLevel_i, f.saturationLevel_z into mydb.cUVLGs_Roderik_PhotoSpecInfo_DR1# from MyDB.All_cUVLGs_Roderik AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll AS o ON n.ObjID = o.ObjID JOIN SpecObjall as spec ON o.specobjid = spec.specobjid JOIN Field as f ON f.fieldid = o.fieldid
